## 9. Prompt Engineering Tips
- Use the "Master NS" trigger to guide the model effectively.
- Structure your prompts with clear descriptors and context.
- Example: "Master NS, a tranquil lake at dawn."

## 10. Batch Generation
```python
for prompt in prompts:
    for i in range(5):  # Modify to generate multiple variations
        image = pipe(prompt + f' variation {i + 1}').images[0]
        image.save(f'/content/drive/MyDrive/outputs/{prompt.replace(" ", "_").replace(",", "").replace(":", "")}_var{i + 1}.png')
```

